unittitle_ssm: United Association of Journeymen and Apprentices of the Plumbing and Pipe Fitting Industry, Local 2 Records
abstract_ssm: United Association of Journeymen and Apprentices of the Plumbing and Pipe Fitting Industry, Local 2 represented workers in the plumbing industry in Manhattan and the Bronx from the late 19th century until the late 1990s.  This collection contains documents and photographs relating to the union's activities from the mid-1940s through early 1990s.  The bulk of the collection is from after 1970.  Materials include legal briefs, case files, correspondence, administrative files, education materials, and photographs.
